@startuml fig-assessment-workflow
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12

title Team project assessment workflow

start
:Submit repository and artefacts;
:Run automated checks\n(formatting, links, tests);
:Validate deterministic network evidence\n(PCAP rules if applicable);
:Review documentation and evidence table;
:Live demonstration and viva discussion;
stop

legend right
  Automated gates reduce ambiguity.
  The viva focuses on reasoning and trade-offs.
endlegend
@enduml
